TopicTitle: One of my stations is suddenly crashing the game upon loading it. Log file included.

Articles.Content:
For some reason, my stations around the Mun is suddenly making the game crash upon switching to it. It almost fully loads but crashes to desktop just as the kerbal portraits begin to load.  Any idea what's going on here?

Full log can be found here.
